{"tid":2148414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟：為中國用户提供服務的承諾堅定不移","createTime":"2020-08-10T02:25:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T03:37:29.000Z","uid":91914,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b320869e0cdd931f58fdce6383b48bae05a2dbc2","tid":2148414,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:25:39.000Z","msg":"格隆匯8月10日丨近日有報道，微軟更新了Microsoft服務協議。根據該協議，如果美國政府對微軟下達禁令，微軟可能無法繼續支持Windows服務，並且不承擔因此引發的任何後果，只會盡最大努力避免影響。對此微軟方面迴應稱，近日某些個別社交媒體對微軟服務條款全球性更新的謠言，不符合事實。我們為中國用户提供服務的承諾堅定不移。"},{"pid":"a1f30c7c4a13f9a9c37f79c72663ecc5b3bc3a0c","tid":2148414,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad057afcc377f84349791cf01e0cb8b8b2c2884","tid":2148414,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6635638b5db0e937632f405359de78050d0187e1","tid":2148414,"uid":73972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"72d1de0065c279f0e3485fb49ab2b2a8d50518e6","tid":2148414,"uid":21432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"「迴應」，呢個係咪特登用字黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d189940710ba62ce72e57721790a76df8769a41e","tid":2148414,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6635638b5db0e937632f405359de78050d01